<BODY>
<body bgcolor="#f5dea2" text="211F99" link="212bcc" vlink="E52F6E">
<H1><center>Resources related to Diabetes Health Economics</center></H1>

<P>
<br>
<br>
<center> This page contains selected materials and compilations related to 
health economic issues in diabetes.  The purpose of the page is to 
maintain an online resource for various materials that I have gathered or 
generated over time.  Others are welcome to use these resources.  I ask, 
though, that you give appropriate attribution to the source (or authors) 
of the materials.  The compilations of papers, cost estimates, and studies 
will vary in their timeliness.  I will be working over time to make all of 
the materials more current.  Your feedback is welcome.</center> <p> <HR>
<p>
<p>
<H2><a name="der">Selected Diabetes Health Economics Resources</a></H2>
<br>
<p>
<H3><IMG SRC="Images/archiv.gif" ALIGN="BOTTOM"> A <A 
HREF="costrefs.html">bibliography</A> of papers on diabetes economics</H3>

<H3><IMG SRC="Images/archiv.gif" ALIGN="BOTTOM"><a 
href="http://www.york.ac.uk/yhpho/cfm/dhedbform.cfm">Diabetes 
Health Economics Resource</a>, a searchable database (1997-forwards) of 
diabetes management-related bibliographic resources</A></H3>

<H3><IMG SRC="Images/dollar.gif" ALIGN="BOTTOM"> Estimates of the economic 
<A HREF="diabcost.html">cost of diabetes</A></H3>

<H3><IMG SRC="Images/drg_db.gif" ALIGN="BOTTOM"> <a
href="econtab.html">Economic evaluation
studies</a> in the diabetes literature</H3>

<H3><IMG SRC="Images/books.gif"" ALIGN="BOTTOM"> <a
href="publications.html">Online Publications</a> on
diabetes economics</H3>

<H3><IMG SRC="Images/teacher.gif" ALIGN="BOTTOM"> Lecture <a 
href="dslides.html">slides</a> on diabetes economics</H3> 
<br><p>
<ul>
<li><img src="Images/newspap.gif" align="left">Other items of note:
<UL>
<LI><a href="http://www.cdc.gov/diabetes/pubs/economics/">The Economics of
Diabetes Mellitus: An Annotated Bibliography</a>, an online publication
from the Centers for Disease Control.

<LI><a 
href="http://www.globalnews.idf.org/2005/07/costs_of_diabet.html">IDF 
estimates of the costs of diabetes</a>, part of the electronic Diabetes 
Atlas.

<LI><a href="http://www.ihe.se/nyhetsblad4-99/diabetes_eng.htm">Diabetes 
and health economics</a>, A summary of recent work at the Swedish
Institute of Health Economics.

<LI><a href="http://ideas.repec.org">IDEAS database</a>, a listing of 
research papers in economics.  Search on diabetes and find several working 
papers related to diabetes.

</UL>
</li>
</ul>
<br><p>
