<p>
<H2><a name="her">Selected Health Economics Resources</a></H2>
<br>
<p>
<ul>
<li> General Collections
<UL>
<LI><A HREF="http://www.exit109.com/~zaweb/pjp">Guide to Health 
Economics, Medicine, and Pharmacy Resources</A>

<LI><a href="http://www.york.ac.uk/inst/crd/crddatabases.htm">NHS Economic 
Evaluation Database</a>, NHS Centre for Reviews and Dissemination

<LI><a href="http://www.york.ac.uk/inst/crd/report4.htm">Guidelines for 
Undertaking Systematic Reviews of Research on Effectiveness</a>, NHS Centre 
for Reviews and Dissemination report on guidelines for reviewing economic 
evaluation studies 
</UL>
</li>
